#### OS functions ####
[Win] + [L] - lock screen
[Win] + [space] - application launcher
[Win] + [V] - open clipboard
[Win] + [shift] + [C] - open color picker
[Win] + [H] - show keybinds.txt
[Win] + [shift] + [Q] - quit hyprland
[Win] + [K] - show keybinds menu
[Win] + [arrow keys] - move focus between windows (also moves cursor)
[Win] + [R] -  Quick runner menu (runs whatever command you give it in a background process)

#### Screenshots ####
[PrintScrn] - switch printscreen output mode (save to file, clipboard or editor)
[Win] + [PrintScrn] - screenshot selectable region
[Win] + [shift] + [PrintScrn] - screenshot selectable window
[Win] + [alt] + [PrintScrn] - screenshot active monitor
[ctrl] + [alt] + [PrintScrn] - screenshot all monitors and stitch them together



#### window management ####
[Win] + [Q] - close focused window (like pressing the X on desktop)
[Win] + [T] - toggle floating on focused window
[Win] + [F] - toggle fullscreen for focused window
[Win] + [P] - toggle pinned for focused window
[Win] + [shift] + [p] - turn focused window into overlay
[Win] + [hold lmb] - move window
[Win] + [hold rmb] - move borders

#### workspaces ####
[Win] + [0-9] - move to workspace x
[Win] + [shift] + [0-9] - move the focused application to workspace x
[Win] + [alt] + [1-9] - set this static layout (wip)
[Win] + [alt] + [0] - return to dynamic layout (default)
[Win] + [scroll] - scroll through active workspaces on the focused monitor


#### programs ####
[Win] + [Enter/Tab] - Open Alacritty (terminal)
[Win] + [E] - open file browser home folder
[Win] + [B] - open web browser (firefox)
[Win] + [O] - open file browser to owncloud folder


#### menus ####
[Win] + [X] - replica windows "power user" menu
[Win] + [Z] - script runner menu containing various utility scripts
[Win] + [C] - quick app menu
[Win] + [A] - Admin utilities menu


#### util ####
[Win] + [shift] + [B] - reload waybar (top bar)
[Win] + [shift] + [W] - reload hyprpaper (wallpaper)

